    "description": "Bolloré Logistics India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Distribution Manager at our Hyderabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Bolloré Logistics India:\nBolloré Logistics India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bolloré Logistics India!",
